platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Set in a snowy Nordic fantasy world, Bad North is about doing the best you can with what youve got. Command troops of archers, swordsmen, and more as you protect a chain of islands from marauders, but one wrong move can prove costly. Tense, slick, and stylish, Bad North is a heady blend of tactical combat, strategic planning, and intuitive controls.
